  "text": "A heuristic matching algorithm was introduced for the DPS-based OPS [CITATION_1] [18]. Simulation results showed that the DPS switch provides low packet loss rates. However, there is no guarantee that the heuristic matching algorithm does provide the optimum solution. Moreover, the performance offset from the optimum solution has not been confirmed.",
